I'll look prettier in the photo.

50
00:04:57,760 --> 00:05:00,160
Yes, you do look good in a skirt.

51
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,960
A daughter is different from a son.

52
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,360
She's so sweet.

53
