173
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,360
It's okay.

174
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,720
You are…

175
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,880
I own a music classroom

176
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,960
