237
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,720
- We'll room with each other.
- Okay.

238
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,560
- Do you want my help?
- No.

239
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:08,680
- Which room?
- Room 166.

240
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,320
166. Good number.

