COLLEGE CAMPAIGN'S MOST POPULAR GIFT

242
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,120
Hello?

243
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,160
Hello, Ruoxin.

244
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,480
I think we can replace

245
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,120
